# 3/13/17 #

Well, tonight I am going to go home crying.  I feel like I ask for help with everything can't do anything on my own. I am afraid I am falling behind and since everything moves so fats that every 10 min I fall behind, is like a day. This really sucks.

I did manage to build about 20% of the project before I was stuck for all the rest. I also managed to do git right. However for the rest of it I feel like I am cheating vs. learning. I jus stare at the screen blankly... then just getting answers from the TAs/Teacher.I'm not even able to get to the reading s it is 8:30pm, my commute is 45 min then I go home and read. Just getting answers from the TAs/Teacher.

Today felt horrible.

Amanda

